                        <div class="col-xs-12">
                            <h3 class="pages-title">全球債市行情</h3>
                            <p>歐美公債殖利率持續走低，各類債券價格普遍上揚，風險性資產表現較優。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-12"><img class="img-responsive" src="~/Content/images/consultant2.jpg"></div>
